modName: Dark Brotherhood to Assassins Creed textures
summary: Texture Replacement for the banners, the black door and the five Tennets.
descriptionHtml:
This Mod changes the banners of the black hand into Assassin\'s Creed Brotherhood banners
It also replaces the hand on the black door with an assassins logo.
The Five Tennets? Who cares about that. Now there is only the creed of the assassins.
Nothing is True,
Everything is Permitted

To Install follo description in the readme.
Known bugs?
None, but if you find some, go on and tell me.
